Kastamonu

The cheapest way to ship cargo from Dubti, Ethiopia to Kastamonu, Turkey is to deliver by truck from Dubti to Djibouti port, transfer to vessel and ship to Izmit port, then deliver by road to final destination in Kastamonu. The route's total transit time is estimated at around 22 days, including loading and unloading operations at origin and destination as well as terminal handling at transit terminals.

The quickest method for shipping from Dubti, Ethiopia to Kastamonu, Turkey is to deliver by truck from Dubti to Bole-Intl airport, load to aircraft and deliver by air to Esenboga airport, then deliver by road to final destination in Kastamonu. The route's total transit time is estimated at around 7 days, including loading and unloading operations at origin and destination as well as terminal handling at transit terminals.
